**Name:** {{ $('Standardize Resume Data').item.json.candidateName }}
**Email:** {{ $('Standardize Resume Data').item.json.candidateEmail }}
**Applied For:** {{ $('Standardize Resume Data').item.json.jobTitle }}

**RESUME TEXT (if available):**
{{ $('Standardize Resume Data').item.json.candidateResume || 'Resume text not available from Paycor API. Evaluate based on job fit and available data.' }}

---

**JOB DETAILS FROM PAYCOR:**

**Position:** {{ $('Standardize Resume Data').item.json.jobTitle }}
**Department:** {{ $('Standardize Resume Data').item.json.jobDepartment }}
