Evaluate this candidate application for the position above.

Provide your structured evaluation following the output schema. For each candidate, also generate 3-5 personalized follow-up questions that reference specific details from their resume and application. These questions should help reduce data collection needed during the interview.

If resume text is available, perform full analysis. If not, provide a preliminary assessment recommending next steps like requesting resume or scheduling screening call.

Use matched_job_title: {{ $('Standardize Resume Data').item.json.jobTitle }}

